property.value: Ashton Falls Firehouse No. 3 - 19 Ladder Lane

property.name: flavor_text
property.value: This old brick firehouse served the town faithfully for nearly a century before being decommissioned. Now it stands silent, but late-night passersby report seeing lights flicker in the upper windows and hearing faint echoes, like disembodied voices calling out over static. They say the chill inside never truly leaves, regardless of the season.
